unittitle_ssm: Records of the Office of Administration and Facilities (Eileen Buckley)
abstract_ssm: The Records of the Office of Administration and Facilities (Eileen Buckley) contain a wide array of information related to the University's property holdings, as well as records relating to the administration of the University as a whole. Included in the collection are materials that document real estate transactions, plans for future development, and maintence of institutional facilities. The collection spans from 1959-1995. The early records in the collection were created by John O'Mara and the later records were created by Lelsie Cohen Berlowitz.
